264
00:25:35,394 --> 00:25:40,058
You didn't win, but you started.

265
00:25:40,166 --> 00:25:43,863
Come on, man.
I know it's you.

266
00:25:52,411 --> 00:25:56,040
Morgan!

267
00:25:56,148 --> 00:25:58,480
Thanks, L.K.

268
00:26:01,053 --> 00:26:03,112
Let's take a walk.

269
00:26:03,222 --> 00:26:06,385
- Rock candy?
- Oh, man, you know I hate rock candy.

270
00:26:06,492 --> 00:26:09,120
Oh, that's right,
because of that one time.

