283
00:26:46,699 --> 00:26:49,964
- Man, I'm a criminal, not a soccer mom!
- Come on, big guy.

284
00:26:50,069 --> 00:26:51,696
CD, DVD.

285
00:26:51,804 --> 00:26:54,671
If you want, I'll even have
Johnny throw some spinners on it.

286
00:26:54,773 --> 00:26:56,536
- Fuck you!
- Or not.

287
00:26:56,642 --> 00:26:59,543
Maybe I'm not making myself clear.

288
00:26:59,645 --> 00:27:03,206
You see, I am a black man.

289
00:27:03,315 --> 00:27:05,340
- Yeah, I got that.
- Okay.

290
00:27:05,451 --> 00:27:08,614
Okay, and that is a minivan.

291
00:27:08,721 --> 00:27:10,780
Right.

292
00:27:10,890 --> 00:27:13,188
