- What happens there stays there.
- What?

328
00:31:15,200 --> 00:31:17,760
The Vegas sticker.

329
00:31:21,807 --> 00:31:25,072
Oh, yeah. It's my brother's car.

330
00:31:27,780 --> 00:31:31,773
