<i>that killin' cops was a good idea.</i>

454
00:46:31,838 --> 00:46:35,239
Genius, that somebody's you.

455
00:46:35,342 --> 00:46:37,833
- You're the one that killed the cops.
- Yeah. Both of 'em.

456
00:46:39,780 --> 00:46:43,307
